## Installation:

$ git clone git://github.com:soulston/vim-bundle.git ~/.vim
$ mkdir -p .vim/bundle
$ git clone git://github.com/gmarik/vundle.git .vim/bundle

Create sylinks:
$ ln -s ~/.vim/.vimrc ~/.vimrc
$ ln -s ~/.vim/.gvimrc ~/.gvimrc (if needed)

Vundle (from vim):
:PluginInstall

